But, in the face of this, the man only makes a magnet.
"Every one says one thing," he says with a bad face.
Ostrava is becoming a large liberalization testing laboratory.
After New Year it will happen with the vast majority of the floors that, in the Czech Republic, were so far under a regulated rental.
Therefore, Aktualně.cz decided to visit the "laboratory" in person.
