When Ensign's spokesman, Jennifer Cooper, announced that Ensign was no longer the subject of a criminal investigation, he said that the senator expected the ethics committee to follow quickly the example of the Department of Justice and complete its investigation.
" Senator Ensign has a desire to continue his difficult work on behalf of the Nevada people," he said.
